Table generation -> rails generate migration TableTitle
The file created is used to create/update/modify/delete Table

Make migration -> rake db:migrate

create_table (plural) :Tables
    add_column :Tables, :title, :type (string, text, integer, float, datetime)

Generate controller -> rails g controller controller(s) page

Models minimum (singular) :
    class Table < ActiveRecord::Base
    end

Form :
    <%= form_tag "/books", method: post/patch/delete do %>
        <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="coucou" />
        <input type="submit" value="Ajouter le livre" />
    <% end %>

* Controller need Model to use Db